Package: yesrouter
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, dpdk (>= 20.11)
Description: YESRouter - High-Performance vBNG/CGNAT Solution
 YESRouter is a carrier-grade virtual Broadband Network Gateway (vBNG)
 with integrated CGNAT, supporting PPPoE, IPoE, and advanced subscriber
 management. Designed for 100Gbps+ throughput with DPDK acceleration.
 .
 Features:
  - PPPoE/IPoE subscriber termination
  - CGNAT with deterministic NAT44
  - IPFIX/NetFlow v9 logging
  - RADIUS AAA integration
  - High availability (active-standby)
  - REST API and CLI management
